==========
 BOTSNACK 
==========
| 

about
-----
| 

:author:  Bart Thate <bthate@gmail.com>
:contact: IRCNET/#dunkbots
:distribution: core
:license: Public Domain
 
| 

description
-----------
| 

give the bot a snack

| 

  eat it 

| 

commands
--------
| 

1) *botsnack*

    :description: give the bot a snack ;] .. botsnack responses can be added with botsnack-add

    :permissions: USER .. CLOUD

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !botsnack
        <output> smikkel ;]


2) *botsnack-add*

    :description: botsnack-add <what> .. add a botsnack response, <nick> can be used to show nick of user giving the command

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !botsnack-add thnx <nick> ;]
        <output> botsnack added


3) *botsnack-del*

    :description: delete entry from botsnack list

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !botsnack-del thnx <nick> ;]
        <output> botsnack thnx <nick> ;] removed


4) *botsnack-list*

    :description: show list of botsnack replies

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !botsnack-list
        <output> []


